About

November 2016 · 1 minute read


A  minimal, responsive  and  light theme  for  Hugo inspired  by Linux
console.

I  Console	https://github.com/mrmierzejewski/hugo-theme-console/blob/master/images/preview.png?raw=true

Installation


i$ mkdir themes	/
i$ cd themes	/
i$ git submodule add https://github.com/mrmierzejewski/hugo-theme-console.git hugo-theme-console	/
i    	/
See the Hugo documentation [1] for more information.

Configuration


Set theme parameter in your config file:

itheme = "hugo-theme-console"	/

